metadata.title: FIGURE 2 in The identity of Pristolepis malabarica (Günther 1864) and Pristolepis procerus Plamoottil 2017, its junior synonym (Anabantiformes: Pristolepididae)
metadata.description: FIGURE 2. CT scan images of the head of Pristolepis malabarica (57.8 mm SL): (a) ventral view of dorsal dentition; (b) dorsal view of ventral dentition; and (c) frontolateral view of head. Note larger projecting parasymphyseal caniniform teeth in upper and lower jaws. Abbreviations: bh-bb tpl- basihyal-basibranchial tooth patch, cb5- ceratobranchial 5, de- dentary, hb3- hypobranchial 3, pal- palatine, pb2- pharyngobranchial 2, pb3- pharyngobranchial 3pmx- premaxilla, ps- parasphenoid, up4- 4th upper pharyngeal toothplate, vo- vomer.
